                <ECUC-NUMERICAL-PARAM-VALUE>
                  <DEFINITION-REF DEST="ECUC-BOOLEAN-PARAM-DEF">/Icu/Icu/IcuOptionalApis/IcuGetTimeElapsedApi</DEFINITION-REF>
